/**
 * COMPREHENSIVE DOCUMENT LIBRARY
 * 
 * This library defines ALL document types that can be generated by the BW Nexus AI system.
 * It covers the full spectrum of global economic, governmental, institutional, and commercial needs.
 * 
 * The system is designed to serve:
 * - Governments (national, regional, municipal)
 * - Sovereign Wealth Funds
 * - Development Finance Institutions (DFIs)
 * - Multilateral Organizations (UN, World Bank, IMF, regional banks)
 * - Private Enterprises (Fortune 500 to SMEs)
 * - NGOs and Foundations
 * - Startups and Innovation Labs
 * - Financial Institutions (banks, insurers, funds)
 * - Academic and Research Institutions
 */

